Scorponok was fairing.  She looked and saw DarkMouse was gone!
"BLAST! Pinned by Matrix know's who and the mouse is gone again." She 
turned back to Scorponok. "Scorponok! Grab the mouse!"  She turned 
and faced the bushes where her enemy was hiding at. "This just isn't 
my day."She shook her head in disgust and kept firing.
